newsitem.title: USA: FGIC qualifies six bond deals for insurance.
newsitem.headline: FGIC qualifies six bond deals for insurance.

text.p: FGIC said Tuesday it qualified six bond deals for insurance slated for competitive sale today.
--Pima County USD #10, Ariz., $19.3 million of school improvement bonds.
--Garrett Co Commr, Md., $4.275 million of general obligation bonds, d.p.
--Washtenaw Community College, Mich., $16.1 million of building bonds.
--Minneapolis Special School District #1, Minn., $16.2 million of COPs.
--Hardeman County, Tenn., $7 million school bonds, d.p.
--Schenectady, N.Y., $10.5 million of public improvement bonds.
